{
  "id": "69a6b79288ca4bd78a66f579",
  "title": "謙遜の文化",
  "created": 1772533652,
  "updated": 1772533739,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69a6b79288ca4bd78a66f579",
      "text": "謙遜の文化",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533652,
      "updated": 1772533652
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b794000000000036908f",
      "text": "[ふーことましろとひよりの会話]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533652,
      "updated": 1772533659
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7eb0000000000369116",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533739,
      "updated": 1772533739
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7980000000000369090",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]（進行係）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533656,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c30000000000369091",
      "text": "はいどーもー！本日のゆるトークテーマは〜「謙遜の文化」！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c30000000000369092",
      "text": "日本人、すぐ「いやいや全然です〜」って言いがち問題な？あれ、もはや国技レベルじゃね？ってやつ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c30000000000369093",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c30000000000369094",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c30000000000369095",
      "text": "ふふ、たしかにね。誰かに褒められても、すぐ打ち消してしまう人、多いわよね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c30000000000369096",
      "text": "「そんなことないです」って、反射みたいに出ちゃう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c30000000000369097",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c30000000000369098",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c30000000000369099",
      "text": "統計的にも、日本は「自己主張を控える」傾向が強い文化圏に分類される。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c3000000000036909a",
      "text": "集団の調和を優先する社会では、自己評価をあえて下げる表現が好まれる傾向がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c3000000000036909b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c3000000000036909c",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c3000000000036909d",
      "text": "出た、ひよりのデータ砲。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c3000000000036909e",
      "text": "でもさー、あれってさ、「本当に自信ない」のと「空気読んでる」っての、どっちなん？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c3000000000036909f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690a0",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690a1",
      "text": "両方ある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690a2",
      "text": "ただ、多くは“自己評価を下げることで場の摩擦を減らす”ための行動。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690a3",
      "text": "いわば、コミュニケーションの潤滑油。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690a4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690a5",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690a6",
      "text": "うんうん。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690a7",
      "text": "自分だけが目立たないようにすることで、相手を立てる気持ちもあるのよね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690a8",
      "text": "「あなたのおかげです」って言葉も、謙遜の一種だと思うわ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690a9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690aa",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690ab",
      "text": "なるほど〜。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690ac",
      "text": "つまり「わたしスゴイでしょ？」ってやると、場がザワる可能性あるから、あえてトーンダウンしてるってことか。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690ad",
      "text": "処世術ってやつ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690ae",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690af",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690b0",
      "text": "そう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690b1",
      "text": "ただし問題もある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690b2",
      "text": "過度な謙遜は、本来の能力評価を下げる可能性がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690b3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690b4",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690b5",
      "text": "あー！それ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690b6",
      "text": "就活で「私なんてまだまだで…」とか言ってたら、「じゃあ不採用で」ってなりかねんやつ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690b7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690b8",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690b9",
      "text": "そうね……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690ba",
      "text": "本当は努力してきたのに、それを言えないのは、少しもったいない気もするわ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690bb",
      "text": "自分を大切にしていない感じがして。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690bc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690bd",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690be",
      "text": "海外の文化では、自己アピールは「事実の提示」として扱われることが多い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690bf",
      "text": "日本では「自慢」と誤解されやすい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690c0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690c1",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690c2",
      "text": "え、文化ガチャじゃん。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690c3",
      "text": "場所変わったら、評価システム変わるやつ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690c4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690c5",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690c6",
      "text": "でもね、私は謙遜そのものが悪いとは思わないの。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690c7",
      "text": "誰かを思いやる気持ちから生まれているなら、とても素敵なことだと思うわ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690c8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690c9",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690ca",
      "text": "同意。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690cb",
      "text": "重要なのは“意図”と“状況”。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690cc",
      "text": "必要な場面では、正確に自己評価を伝える能力も必要。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690cd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690ce",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690cf",
      "text": "つまりさ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690d0",
      "text": " 友だちに褒められた →「そんなことないよ〜」でほっこり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690d1",
      "text": " 面接で実績聞かれた →「実はこれやりました」ってちゃんと言う",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690d2",
      "text": "って、使い分け大事ってこと？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690d3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690d4",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690d5",
      "text": "合理的。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690d6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690d7",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690d8",
      "text": "ええ、とても自然な考え方ね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690d9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690da",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690db",
      "text": "でもさー、なんで日本ってこんなに謙遜テンプレあるんだろ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690dc",
      "text": "「つまらないものですが」とか。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690dd",
      "text": "絶対つまらなくないやつ渡してるよね？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690de",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690df",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690e0",
      "text": "歴史的背景。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690e1",
      "text": "上下関係を重視する社会構造では、へりくだる表現が礼儀とされた。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690e2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690e3",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690e4",
      "text": "相手を尊重する言葉づかいの一部なのよね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690e5",
      "text": "本音では「心を込めました」でも、形としては控えめに言う。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690e6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690e7",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690e8",
      "text": "なるほどね〜。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690e9",
      "text": "つまり、「自分を小さくする」ってより、「相手を大きくする」って発想か。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690ea",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690eb",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690ec",
      "text": "良い要約。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690ed",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690ee",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690ef",
      "text": "ふーこ、今日はまとめ上手ね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690f0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690f1",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690f2",
      "text": "え、やめてやめて、照れるから。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690f3",
      "text": "いやいや全然ですよ〜（棒）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690f4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690f5",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690f6",
      "text": "それが今まさに謙遜。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690f7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690f8",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690f9",
      "text": "ふふ、かわいいわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690fa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690fb",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690fc",
      "text": "くっ……無限ループ入った。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690fd",
      "text": "じゃあ最終まとめいくよ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690fe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c300000000003690ff",
      "text": "謙遜ってさ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c30000000000369100",
      "text": "✔ 空気を守るバリア",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c30000000000369101",
      "text": "✔ 相手を立てる優しさ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c30000000000369102",
      "text": "✔ でも使いすぎると自分が見えなくなるリスクあり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c30000000000369103",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c30000000000369104",
      "text": "って感じ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c30000000000369105",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c30000000000369106",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c30000000000369107",
      "text": "概ね妥当。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c30000000000369108",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c30000000000369109",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c3000000000036910a",
      "text": "大切なのは、「自分を下げること」じゃなくて、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c3000000000036910b",
      "text": "「相手と心地よく関わること」なのかもしれないわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c3000000000036910c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c3000000000036910d",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c3000000000036910e",
      "text": "おお〜、名言出た！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c3000000000036910f",
      "text": "じゃあ今日はここまで！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c30000000000369110",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c30000000000369111",
      "text": "みんなもさ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c30000000000369112",
      "text": "謙遜しすぎて自分ログ消しちゃわないようにね！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c30000000000369113",
      "text": "自己肯定、適量でいこ〜！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c30000000000369114",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6b7c30000000000369115",
      "text": "（三人、ゆるく笑いながら帰り道へ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772533699,
      "updated": 1772533699
    }
  ]
}